        <mxCell id="qOhjqbUxFWDzHHpB3DUN-59" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fillColor=#dae8fc;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;assessment.st&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;You are the Orchestrator for Application {appNum}.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Context: Amount ${amount} | Address: {address} | Token: {secureSsn}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;### Instructions:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;1. **Delegate**: Call the &#39;senior-underwriter&#39; sub-agent.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;**CONTEXT**: (Loan Amount: {amount}, SSN: {secureSsn}).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;2. **Finalization**: The underwriter will return a JSON object containing the &#39;result&#39; and &#39;comment&#39;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;3. **Action**: Pass that JSON object back to the user exactly as received. Do NOT perform any additional analysis.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;### Output:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Return the &#39;DecisionResult&#39; JSON provided by the underwriter.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
